{"tid":2118182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【壹週刊追查白衣人 鄉黑兇記者 田雞東：唔聽話就藤條炆豬肉","createTime":"2020-07-21T10:08:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T11:33:39.000Z","uid":47536,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a0c7506029c0f09e8085c8b83a6f2f184a5543f0","tid":2118182,"uid":47536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T10:08:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/121625551334730/posts/1635886459908624/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F121625551334730%2Fposts%2F1635886459908624%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj%2BdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=e8be413d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/121625551334730/posts/1635886459908624/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n721恐襲，一班無差別襲擊市民的白衣人，明顯涉及14K及和勝和的元朗鄉黑勢力。事件雖然已一年，但香港人仍然無法忘記。而我們亦嘗試追訪事件中幾個關鍵人物，要求他們回應事件。<br />\n<br />\n啲鄉黑串過馬撚，連記者都摷到差佬竟然拉唔到人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Respect記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b86e618e9ccbd450d2964a6efb9eee7a2ce277a9","tid":2118182,"uid":47536,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T10:10:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2KYj56z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2KYj56z.png&h=c517c18a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"85965ec75d7576a332dfc487fe7abe58cf84617f","tid":2118182,"uid":221171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T10:17:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ewjvtmZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FewjvtmZ.jpg&h=d8dd9f86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Cm9JVj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Cm9JVj.jpg&h=cba2898b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TVMNvAk.jp